springboot+druid datasource

一.运行应用必备条件:
1开发工具eclipse/STS
2安装maven
3安装git
4安装mysql数据库

二.SQL script:
-- Table structure for `customer_profile_info`
-- ----------------------------
DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `customer_profile_info`;
CREATE TABLE `customer_profile_info` (
  `status` varchar(1) NOT NULL,
  `password` varchar(15) NOT NULL,
  `user_name` varchar(20) NOT NULL,
  `user_id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  PRIMARY KEY (`user_id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=2 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

-- ----------------------------
-- Records of customer_profile_info
-- ----------------------------
INSERT INTO `customer_profile_info` VALUES ('1', 'testing1234', 'admin', '1');

三.github url:
https://github.com/yiduhuangyan/springboot-druid.git

四.启动后访问的地址
http://localhost:8080/test/profileinfo
http://localhost:8080/druid/index.html




